				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>I&#8217;ve said this &#8220;in real world&#8221; but I absolutely love this story! It is possibly my favourite of yours, layered, beautifully told, just awesome. I know you want criticism, and maybe I can get behind that &#8220;no need for actual blood&#8221; thing, but&#8230; it is a very beautiful story, and I really really like its 3-fold interpretation of the theme &#8211; the gargoyle outside the window, the girl outside of society, and the narrator outside the story. </p>
<p>Thank you very much for this!</p>
